05:46.380 --> 05:47.813
And for the record,

05:47.860 --> 05:49.122
Davis was never charged.

05:49.170 --> 05:50.649
But you know that.

05:50.690 --> 05:52.476
- Of course.
- Mm-hmm.

05:52.520 --> 05:55.080
But you did settle
the civil case with
that woman?

05:55.130 --> 05:56.563
Melina Galoudian.

05:56.610 --> 05:58.305
Yes, we did.

05:58.350 --> 06:01.001
It was tough,
but we came out
of It stronger.

06:02.750 --> 06:04.047
